description: Join Sadie for an inspiring and incredible journey into your loving and strong Warrior Nature! You will learn to unlock your authenticity, clarity and health in just a few awesome sessions. Sadie, one of the most in-demand yoga and empowerment leaders in the world, and someone who is highly skilled at fear-busting and moving forward to create her passionate best life, leads you through the exact steps to take to find your own best self, and then rock it from the inside out. Includes daily yoga practice, new anatomy and alignment tips that will double the effectiveness of your yoga practice (better strength, calorie burn, flexibility, tone and detox). You'll learn to let go of what's no longer serving your greatness, and how to stop playing small and safely step into your truth. It's a blast!
title: The Warrior Within: Empower Your Yoga and Inner Strength!
